name: Calculation
definition: actual execution of some computation, computational process, or operation that was scheduled or triggered by something
label: calculation

name: Occurrence
explanatoryNote: Each occurrence has a date time stamp, which identifies when the event occurred, and, optionally, a location (possibly virtual), that identifies where the occurrence happened.
label: occurrence
definition: happening of an OccurrenceKind, i.e., an event

name: CalculationEvent
label: calculation event
definition: kind of event that is either scheduled or triggered by something, such as a related financial event, that causes a calculation to be performed

name: OccurrenceKind
definition: classifier that specifies the general nature of an occurrence (event)
explanatoryNote: As types (or categories) of events, OccurenceKinds do not happen; OccurenceKinds describe Occurrences which happen and exemplify an OccurenceKind. As occurrences are things that actually happen, they have an actual date where as OccurenceKinds do not have an actual date.
label: occurrence kind

name: OccurrenceBasedDate
explanatoryNote: The 'hasDateValue' property of an OccurrenceBasedDate is not set until the Occurrence happens. The 'triggeredBy' property relates an OccurrenceBasedDate to the OccurrenceKind that gives the meaning of the OccurrenceBasedDate.
definition: calculated date that is defined with respect to the occurrence of some occurrence kind
label: occurrence-based date

name: hasEventDateValue
label: has event date value
definition: identifies a date or date and time value associated with an event (occurrence)

name: isOutputFrom
label: is output from
definition: indicates post condition or other product of some activity, process, system, report, analysis, etc.

name: hasEventDate
label: has event date
definition: identifies a date associated with an event (occurrence)

name: hasOccurrence
definition: identifies events of a given occurrence kind, typically as they occur in a schedule
label: has occurrence

name: isInputTo
definition: indicates a precondition, requirement, or other contribution (e.g., data) to some activity, process, system, report, analysis, etc.
label: is input to

name: isTriggeredBy
label: is triggered by
explanatoryNote: An OccurrenceBasedDate is triggered by an Occurrence that exemplifies the OccurrenceKind.

name: hasOutput
definition: relates something (e.g. an occurrence) to something that is the result of some activity or process
label: has output

name: hasInput
definition: relates something (e.g. an occurrence) to something that is used as an input to some activity or process
label: has input
